{"tid":2235230,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"余文樂「又」不知不覺做左港獨","createTime":"2020-10-08T13:27:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T14:20:11.000Z","uid":42246,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b8051515d9b1af34c6f3b108c90b8cafe6674c09","tid":2235230,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T13:27:24.000Z","msg":"佢一日上左兩次微博熱搜<br />\n首先單野係咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XAifQgE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXAifQgE.png&h=5e59e633&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bvT3Y90.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbvT3Y90.jpg&h=eeb7981d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vOW5s3k.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvOW5s3k.png&h=36ee2a17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢個助理疑似講左句「我地從來唔排隊」<br />\n但lok哥本人比人屌港獨屌到傻<br />\n<br />\n咁上左微博熱搜 佢個助理就要出來解話<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/70WQEaE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F70WQEaE.png&h=42649b70&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8qDjxvF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8qDjxvF.png&h=df05b52f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yMhwoCk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyMhwoCk.png&h=258e8042&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n都係比人屌港獨屌到傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最搞笑係佢篇解話 打左一大段個過程<br />\n但班小粉紅只睇到佢篇野<br />\n用「特殊節日假」唔用「國慶節日假」（已經改返）<br />\n又比人屌到傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DJKKJDf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDJKKJDf.png&h=5f1ed2aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n支持香港用國安法調查LOK <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fd2f1f4bb9525a19e359dfd7cdc17af4cfa4f76","tid":2235230,"uid":42246,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T13:29:01.000Z","msg":"lok 支持5大的<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab950d0cdcfc6d10118dcf884a9638a68a84c2dc","tid":2235230,"uid":42246,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T13:30:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RwSHvjK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRwSHvjK.png&h=48429922&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OLcHvjK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOLcHvjK.png&h=6d93b19d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n批鬥就係中國人既優良基因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc14e3f816a6be2aed57b7742278bbe5487d77c9","tid":2235230,"uid":145273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T13:31:22.000Z","msg":"即係班小粉